nodes.text: Ytterbium was an explosive material vital in the production of laser cannons. In Thermal wells Ytterbium was used as a stabilizer to make the baradium in the explosive less hazardous. Ytterbium was found in rich quantities in the Sarrahban system.
Ytterbium in reality is a metallic element. This may or may not be the same substance as the ytterbium of the Star Wars universe.
